Eq admitted.
refl admitted.
eq_rect admitted.
Inferred type: forall (A : Set) (x y : A), Eq A x y -> Eq A y x
Extracted: fun (A : *) (x y : A) (h : Eq A) => eq_rect [A] x [Eq A] (refl [A] x) y h
Extracted: fun (A : *) (x y z : A) (hxy hyz : Eq A) => eq_rect [A] y [Eq A] hxy z hyz
Extracted: fun (A B : *) (f : A -> B) (x y : A) (h : Eq A) => eq_rect [A] x [Eq B] (refl [B] (f x)) y h
Extracted: fun (A P : *) (x y : A) (h : Eq A) (p : P) => eq_rect [A] x [P] p y h
